Subject: [PATCH 24/25] UI rebuild stage 3: dedicated HOME door
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Landing on Diagnose no longer lights the REFERENCE door. dumps becomes a
pinned HOME button above the six job doors (not a member of any job, so
JOB_OF.dumps is undefined and no door highlights); it's excluded from the
Advanced drawer. REFERENCE's primary is now backups (gets a stable
backups-tab root testid). Nav guard gains a HOME test — 16 nav tests green.
